📋 DESCRIPTION
Compute P_med, a scale-free probabilistic effect size
for causal mediation analysis. Provides interpretable
measures of mediation strength.

Version: 0.2.0 (GitHub release 2026-06-11, non-CRAN; pins medfit@v0.3.0)
  — adds method="mbco" + parallel (joint) P_med
  — 2026-06-14: dev→main release PR #4 merged; main was stale (v0.1.0/v0.2.0
    had been tagged off dev, integration PR never opened). main now = 0.2.0.
  — 2026-06-14: r-universe registry flipped probmed dev→main (builds from main).
  — 2026-06-14: Windows quarto-vignette failure fixed (PR #5/#6, on main); CI now
    runs R-CMD-check+test-coverage on dev (PR #7) so failures surface before release.
    NOTE: workflow trigger change is on dev; main syncs it at the next dev→main PR.

